Located on the beach & Broadwalk, Latitudes Restaurant and Bar welcomes you to Hollywood Beach with dining and drinking along the Atlantic Ocean all year long.
Find your latitude at our oceanfront restaurant and bar on the famed South Florida Hollywood Broadwalk to enjoy what Hollywood has to offer.
Come casual and enjoy craft beer and cocktails, and share some apps and entrees at the oceanfront bar.  Engage in the people-watching along the
Hollywood Broadwalk,
a 2.5 mile pedestrian promenade.
Serving breakfast, lunch, dinner, and libations from our all-day menu while offering a wide range of cuisine for everyone day and night.  Outdoor and indoor seating available at our Hollywood FL dining destination.  We even offer great space for holiday parties, reunions, birthday parties and more!
Heading out to catch a flight?  Our Hollywood Beach Broadwalk Restaurant is only 5 miles from the
Fort Lauderdale Airport
, FLL, so get yourself checked-in and/or stop here for a drink and some food before your next destination.
Monday – Friday: Ala carte breakfast menu is available from 6:30AM-10:45AM, buffet is open until 11:00AM.
Saturday- Sunday: Ala carte breakfast menu is available from 6:30AM-10:45AM, buffet is open until 12:00Noon.
Lunch / Dinner: Sunday - Thursday from 11:00AM - 10:00PM and Friday - Saturday from 12:00PM -11:00PM.
Bar Hours
:  Sun-Thursday serving from 9:00AM to 11:00PM  and Friday - Saturday until 12:00AM.
